event,"heh some things never change...that would be boys

on to another subject i had an interesting night at work mon night...i had my first spray job...i was unaware that we would be spraying...they got me on the job and then i realized what is a 1 night 1 person job has 2 ppl...yeah then mark was like u know your sprayin this out tonight right i was like huh?  oh geez it was funny...gravy job but still first spray job so i was nervous mark was a good teacher tho...i cant complain...everyone was like you didnt spary him???how come???so maybe next time ill have to spray him...haha yeah my fingers hurt some kinda bad ok well not all of them just my two ring fingers from riding...jig was so heavy in the bridle sun night that he gave me these two huge blisters even with gloves on...it sux they hurt sooo bad but theres not much i can do about that now.  um lets see...hmm i think i may have to go take a walk and check the horses theres alot of whinnying out there...ill give them a few min and see...hope the babies are ok...hmm quiet now...idk wow im SOOO tired idk why.  looks like germany in the spring for a couple of weeks!!! i cant wait this is gonna be awesome.  passport in hand ready to go! im gonna have a grand time and i know steph  will to... but seriously ok i gtg check them theyre still up in arms about something..."

event,"well plans turned out well um i kinda dunno how to feel about them...saw alota ppl i havent seen in quite a long time and alota  ppl i never wanted to ever see again in my life...wow yeah old crushes too haha kept my distance tho...yeah so bath was uh interesting ...the great tucker hunt lol too funny...some people will go for anything...shes thinks your pretty hot...not into that sorta thing? how come....oh here let me wipe that up for you...***GROPE, GROPE***my god...wow is all i have to say i mean yeah idk if i wanna go back down there...must have been a HUGE disappointment hehe oh well i dont care poor mark ""how can you drink this"" ha i think u did kinda drive him off...i was REALLY hoping he was gonna stick around cause DAMN i knew what those other two had planned for me and i didnt want to be part of it...close to getting dragged into it too thank god for will power.  So any calls today steph...if so sober i hope...my tummys def feeling the wine oh lordy wow havent had that stuff in awhile wow...wasnt good stuff either ick oh well give me a call later i gtg get the horses finished and get ready for a lesson ttyl"

event,"wow so many things going on lately...saw beau diddles parents the other day nice looking dogs and theyre both so smart what happened to him???lol they said he was the biggest pup of them all wow makes me feel kinda special!  haha yeah theyve got another litter...and ive got another dog on the way...yeah thats what i said i got a full sis to bo...stupid me oh well...she wicked cute and soooo calm! what a sweetie i flipped her over on her back and held her in my lap and she passed right out it was so cute!!! cant wait now...daddy doesnt know yet but he'll just have todeal with it...shes a cutie and i need a female to cross with doufus for some pups!  oh i cant wait...money maker right there i hope maybe i can get them registered with ckc or something...idk we will see cant wait....yay!   haha well anyways i gtg take care of chores and get ready for the festival de la egg in ptown...cant wait SUCH fun ... no sarcasm there..."

event,"u know what that victorias secret idea is becoming more of a reality now...i think thatll be my 3rd one lol right on my ass or maybe just below the belt...idk yet...close enough...ANYWAYS il ove my new one its so cute!!! undecided about if I think its finished or if i wanna add more to it but idk hmm ill take a poll and go from there...anyways yeah thats my news for now cant wait this is addicting lol hmm yeah oh oh yeah vicys sec in glow in the dark haha oh the fun..."

event,"wow hehe ive officially become a kitten factory/farm...ppl are calling left and right for kittens!! i cant believe it i thought itd be a waste of a stamp to put the kittens in the uncle henrys but apparently not! wow like lets see 6 calls already and this is just thurs! hmm i should start charging money for them i could make some damn good cash!!!haha nah thatll be for when we get the siamese and persian crosses on the calicos lol i cant wait lol wow hmm is my phone ringing again? omg lol wow sappy music grr cant find the cd kinda bummin.  oh well"

event,"oh lordy...you all know im fucked up anyways so i dont care...Peter S. Beagles book ""The Last Unicorn"" will have a new video coming out...real ppl real horses etc...the director (Geoffry Murphy i think) was one that worked closely on and with the director of the lord of the rings this is SOOO damn exciting...i love the book love the cartoon and of course i love unicorns always had that fetish im soo excited now...and i found this website thats got the complete soundtrack of the cartoon they did back yrs ago oh my im excited.  i cant wait should come out the fall of 2006...idk tho theyve got an arab i think that theyll be using for the unicorn...i dont like that idea...i like arabs but andalusians and lusitanos are much better at playing mytical creatures.  im gonna have to write and call to make sure they get the right breed in the movie cause itll make or break the movie u know lol oh i cant wait now!!!yay im gonna have to go watch the movie again now...yay!"

event,"wowee hitching huh thats uhm interesting i almost feel bad enough to go pick them up but well uhm not quite..lol...idk if sven was there that night or not if so he was either the creepy one who patted my head or the short funny one in the kitchen that tackled tuck...hmm that one was kinda cute but idk im kinda scared now...u may be on your own steph idk about this one i may have to make myself scarce...or at least really hammered.  anyways yeah...

hmm new tattoo this fri im kinda scared very unsure if i want this or not...i mean its permi...no going back...scary thing....idk this was so much easier drunk i mean i picked what i wanted right away...haha unsure of exactly what it is but yeah oh oh haha i showed a couple ppl at work my tat on my back and first reaction...flying monkey like the ones on wizard of ozz lol that and a bat lol my god...anyways yeah now that im thinking hehe this is cute yeah some ppl refer to and tease me about the middle name...victoria and call me victoria serect...hmm im thinkin now lol idk how serious about it i am but how bout victoria secret right on my ass???hmm interesting conversation peice lol j/k i doubt i could go thru with that one...god the first thing tho that came out of jerrys mouth when i mentioned i was getting another tattoo was ""WHERE"" oh god it was sooo damn funny.  i mean just the sort of thing jerry would say.  wow.  anyways yeah this sat will be interesting like i said im prolly gonna hve to vacate the area if get too scared if it had been glenn or even dolphin i coulda delt ok with it but strange ppl i dont know oh lordy. wow well enough for now i got ponies to ride."

event,"haha interesting night at work last night oh geez...back up lead man turned out to be mark bubar funny guy...ive had the ""P10 award for the night"" 2 nights in a row and well ive had enough of bein a bull so past couple ive been lucky eough to be in a room that has a door is at the top of the stairs in a secluded area and that locks!  fun stuff there too bad...well we wont get into that...but yeah...talked to bubar alot last night funny stuff...told him about the ""stupid boys"" incident(s) and of course the dumb yellow vw that went by my house one time and a few other stories...""oh geez i dont ever wanna make you or your friends angry my god""...we're cool right oh so funny.

the dog IS going to die im certain of it...came home and u know its not like he could chew up 2 shoes of the same pair...NO one from 2 different pairs...motherfuckers got a short lifespan ahead of him...i mean the plug for the kitchen sink how...why the fuck...jesus...idk anymore i think we're gonna get one of those training collars...hopefully those will work but this is bo we're talkig about here...
overtime tonight...bubar doesnt think i can make it 6 nights in a row...quite frankly i dont know if i can make it 6 either but im gonna give it a shot...
well theres lots to do and i need a shower and maybe another nap so till whenever..."

event,"ok doufus is a great dog...the quiet angry chicken type...he'll be there and guard you when it matters but dont ask him to socialize...the puppy he just well he doesnt understand that you cant love everyone...doufus house broken perfectly...puppy 6 months of training still having accidents.  doufus can keep track of his thoughts...puppy doesnt know what hes doing at any given time.  doufus chewed kindlin as a pup...puppy chews everything he can reach...if its not 100lbs or something other than furniture its game!...he is going to die...i have like 3-4 pairs of choes that have somehow survived this long, clothing oh oh thats fun to rip and shred, magazines, boxes, SCISSORS????WTF grrr anyways the puppy is going to die im certain of it and if that sets my mood then well i just may move on from there..."

event,"funny thing the other night was like 20 Questions on my eating habits at work...everyone just bombarded me with questions and i was just like wow i gotta leave to much attention focused on me and WAY too many questions. so yeah we had covered the fact that im not into trying new things...well...i ventured into unknown territory today...i tried hommus...and guess what...I love it! so weird taken my mind of the whole franchise thingy goin on and the other stuff goin on...but funny thing anyways not a whole lots goin on just same old same old getting restless with life right now for some reason but yeah now that the company owns me ill at least be able to pay my bills so thatll be good...hmm still planning revenge tho...im getting less and less bitter for some reason...scary thing  i mean not that i trust anyone at all or ever will but just not so bitter..."

event,"wow...wow...hmm no calls recently from anyone entertaining...well jason text messaged me but nothing really came of it...gotta head to work soon...this sux...yeah tattoo wed im kinda scared decisions are so much easier when drunk...yeah idk...but yeah...hmm so tuck called huh funny stuff right there...too much. oh yes oh yes...i bleached my hair with an interesting twist on color...supposed to be orange but its not quite...more like a rosy pink color very pretty none the less...just ended up that way due to lack of the color we needed so we experimented...came out nice tho blonde with rosy hightlights...rather lowlights....itll be an adjustment but i think ill grow to like it...ok well im gonna get ready for work so this is the end of this till now...planning revenge on dave sometime soon i hope...more on that later"

event,"what a wasted day did nothing...i think my meds are um not quite what i should be on...i mean a couple tiny sips of alcohol shouldnt sned me into being dizzy all day the next day with a head ache and my whole jaw aching...

event,"boy boys boys...mommy always told me they were trouble and guess what?...she was right...nothing but trouble...but it usually hits them the hardest...oh well we will see what comes of this...
